   is permitted free of charge, PROVIDED THAT the article above is
   cited in any resulting publication or public artifact.

2. Redistribution of the dataset (in whole or in substantial part) must
   retain this notice and the citation requirement, and must link back
   to the canonical repository:
   https://github.com/BrandNewJimZhang/OneAtmosphere-LLM

3. Commercial use or commercial redistribution of the dataset requires
   prior written permission from the authors.

4. Model responses contained in the dataset (columns such as gpt-4o,
   deepseek-v3, qwen2.5-*) were generated by the respective third-party
   models; their reuse may additionally be subject to the terms of the
   corresponding model providers.

